# Primary Developer Admin

- Treat `diazites.ai@gmail.com` as the primary Diazites developer/admin account.
- This account should be able to manage users, platform settings, plan upgrades/downgrades, feature/tab access, and overall platform administration.
- When changing auth, onboarding, dashboard routing, billing, entitlements, or admin access logic, preserve this account's platform-admin behavior and avoid making it behave like a normal customer account.
